{"tid":1189151,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"高麗大學花費近25萬美金 邀請嘉賓參加慶典","createTime":"2019-06-06T16:07:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-07T21:12:08.000Z","uid":1086,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"cf8fa0187831e4eb5ca396615bce4b83d90ceddf","tid":1189151,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T16:07:07.000Z","msg":"高麗大學的校園報紙The HOANS最近報導了有關學校花在上次大學慶典的金額而引起爭議。他們之前舉行的大學慶典邀請了金延宇，請夏，Lovelyz, SEVENTEEN, 10cm和Daybreak來表演。<br />\n<br />\n他們為了這次慶典花費了大約25萬美金。相比<span style=\"color: red;\">延世大學只花了13萬美金就請到IU, Beenzino, Zico, TWICE, and Red Velvet</span>，學生批評支出金額太高了。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n根據採訪，學校想要邀請好的主唱來配合慶典的主題-電影。「考慮到行程和費用，我們可以請Psy來表演，但是為了配合主題，所以我們請了金延宇。」更令人震驚的是，他們還說「真實情況是，Henry主動要到我們的慶典來無償表演，但是因為和慶典主題不搭配，所以被拒絕了。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rnPY8X8wmNA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DrnPY8X8wmNA&d=KA2pTlu%2BoVpRwWZcRxs8e4eNTHq1rgEicHo%2BkVhR8rs%3D&h=484cfba2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rnPY8X8wmNA</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rXCKBNy3VdM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DrXCKBNy3VdM&d=KA2pTlu%2BoVpRwWZcRxs8e4eNTHq1rgEicHo%2BkVhR8rs%3D&h=41fa150d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rXCKBNy3VdM</a>"},{"pid":"1f78fe460e48707139fb7d49499cd194959a08d6","tid":1189151,"uid":34489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T16:07:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://emojipedia-us.s3.dualstack.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/thumbs/72/apple/198/face-with-rolling-eyes_1f644.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Femojipedia-us.s3.dualstack.us-west-1.amazonaws.com%2Fthumbs%2F72%2Fapple%2F198%2Fface-with-rolling-eyes_1f644.png&h=7096e9d0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"62e2c33b36809d39e36d241887f65d2ce31f8b07","tid":1189151,"uid":138740,"like":16,"disl